{"tid":2289243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［識貨］日本木造建築工藝將被列入非物質文化遺產","createTime":"2020-11-17T06:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T11:25:54.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e176805fd13749e83628d24fd2f66e9024683350","tid":2289243,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"日本文化廳11月17日宣佈，聯合國教科文組織（UNESCO）的評估機構建議將宮殿木匠和泥瓦匠等繼承的「傳統建築工匠技藝　旨在繼承木造建造物的傳統技術」列為非物質文化遺產。預計在12月14～19日在線舉行的聯合國教科文組織政府間委員會會議上正式決定列入。<br />\n<br />\n       對象為木工和泥瓦匠等17個領域的技術。除了瓦屋頂、茅草屋頂、門窗和榻榻米的製作之外，還包括對建築物的外觀和內飾進行的裝飾、上色和塗漆。利用木、草和土等天然材料，建造能承受地震和颱風的結構，這些技術被認為支撐著以奈良法隆寺為代表的日本傳統建築文化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/11/17/142745_cea4ff2624086b18ec0f60aafce79363.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F11%2F17%2F142745_cea4ff2624086b18ec0f60aafce79363.png&h=99a0f60f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/11/17/142749_b62441d4bd8242fccd6dd57290b3c1ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F11%2F17%2F142749_b62441d4bd8242fccd6dd57290b3c1ff.png&h=fd3687e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nikkei.com/politicsaeconomy/politicsasociety/42780-2020-11-17-14-17-26.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nikkei.com%2Fpoliticsaeconomy%2Fpoliticsasociety%2F42780-2020-11-17-14-17-26.html&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4y1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=a479ca0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nikkei.com/politicsaeconomy/politicsasociety/42780-2020-11-17-14-17-26.html</a>"},{"pid":"f84f57c590934f9e565f7ea4ce75c5b93d8bcbcf","tid":2289243,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:22:33.000Z","msg":"連中國要維修/起番啲傳統建築都要搵日本人幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7088daeda4f4abf625270d0f9355c9d5bfb444","tid":2289243,"uid":30868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:25:54.000Z","msg":"日本d 木屋勁香"}]}